This is version 4 of surf_metal_prison

Some new features:

the map is totally retextured
lights are now added to the map
grenades behind the spawns
invisible wall behind portal, so you will fly always in one direction
2 sniper weapons on the letters "made by RHL#[NL]Robbiedoes". 

and that's it. 

if you found any bugs please report them to: gangstarobbie@gmail.com, the same for when you want to change the map, please first ask for permisson.
